Detailed Description

Class for holding a last client type for a user.

When packed into or from a packet UserIDKey looks like this.

{tabular}{lll} Pos & Size & Destription \ pos & 4 bytes & TYPE_LAST_CLIENT \ +4 & 2 bytes & Total size in bytes \ +6 & 4 bytes & TYPE_LAST_CLIENT \ +10 & 2 bytes & Total size in bytes \ +12 & 4 bytes & ID \ +16 & string & client type \ +x & string & client type options \ +X & string & version \ +X & string & extra \ +X & string & origin \ {tabular}
